data.description: Beautiful elegance best describes this lovely 5-bedroom home. Spacious rooms are strategically positioned throughout, making it feel even larger than its 4000 sq.ft. The open kitchen includes a double oven and large walk-in pantry. Primary suite, guest bed with full bath and study are downstairs. 3 additional bedrooms 2 full baths, and secondary living room upstairs. You will find wood flooring throughout. All the bedrooms have walk in closets.  The huge backyard includes an elegant covered patio with lighting and ceiling fans, a paved area for basketball, solid play set, all enclosed with a 6’ boar-on-board privacy fence. You will appreciate the space provided in the 3-car garage. Welcome home!
